# No Claude / Anthropic contributor attribution

Never add Claude, Anthropic, or any AI assistant as a project contributor or co-author.

Forbidden in commits, PRs, README, AUTHORS, team pages, metadata, or docs:

- `Co-Authored-By: Claude …`
- `Co-Authored-By: …@anthropic.com`
- “Generated with Claude”, “Assisted by Claude”, or similar credit lines
- Listing Claude / Anthropic in contributor, team, or acknowledgements lists

Commit messages and PR bodies must credit only human team members the user names, or omit tooling credits entirely.
